# DA-2: Abstraction by Business Meaning
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: New class/module creation

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- Business Meaning: Real-world concept the system models.
- Abstraction Level: Degree to which implementation details are hidden in favor of business-oriented concepts.

ENFORCE: Abstractions must reflect business domain concepts, not technical convenience.
PROHIBIT: Abstractions created purely for code reuse without business context.
ON VIOLATION: Escalate to Domain Model Guardian Skill; suggest realignment.
